{
  "stem": "6736.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In 1943, when they liquidated the ghetto, that time was Emalia even more important, because, instead of going to Plaszow to concentration camp, Oskar Schindler built barracks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he made his own camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in that camp, nobody beat you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You were not hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You were treated half-decent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In 1944, Poles start run-- the Russians start taking over Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were already in Tarnow, next large town to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he had orders to liquidate his Emalia factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was a Madritsch who was making uniforms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He also had order to liquidate his factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And Madritsch-- he wanted to do something with Madritsch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But Madritsch said, I did as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he washed his hands.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the good part of Oskar Schindler-- the outstanding thing-- is that in August-- he was a very rich man.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He had a lot of money from the black market, and from presents that he got from people to let them in the Emalia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That he could have said, I'm going to take my wife, and maybe a girlfriend, and go to Switzerland or go to Germany-- deep in Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I did for the Jews as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But he didn't do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was determined to save the Jews-- at least his Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So he went to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It  was a bombed out factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he went to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he told them in Berlin that, if they let him have his people-- that they are engineers, sheet metal workers, and all good mechanics-- if they let him rebuild this factory, he going to be able  in a few months to make ammunition for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But in '44, in August, the factory was not ready.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the papers did not come through from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
